	(text "When PushToRing is active and 20Hz is high,\n  then the ring generator is running and\n  the Enable_HV+ is alternating with Enable_HV-\n  at a 20 Hz rate.\nWhen idle,\n  then the HV+ should be off (low)\n  and the HV- is also off (high)."
